 "name": "RPlog_Retribution_-_Evacuation_of_the_Orphans",
 "title": "Retribution: Evacuation of the Orphans",
 "summary": "In the formal, eerily quiet Parliamentary District of Coruscant, New Republic personnel -- the pilots Aramis and Kyrin Sh'vani, the Marine Vengan, and Munch -- move to evacuate a group of orphaned children trapped amid the fighting for the capital. With the district's lawns deserted and its residents lying low, the team works against the clock and the surrounding war to spirit the vulnerable children to safety. The log follows the tense, compassionate effort to get the orphans clear of the battle zone.",
